Integrates the PartsList and WiringController.  Scans its target for certain widgets (buttons, text, sliders, lists, colorChoosers and... the Elephant), and presents them in a spreadsheet-style partslist.

See the comment and example connections in 
    http://www.lively-web.org/users/Dan/Fab1.html
    
Under construction and not yet integrated with all widgets nor the current connection defaults
